  <!-- 1.8.5 -->
  <section class="docs-getstarted-section" id="v1.8.5">
    <h2>v1.8.5</h2>
    <p><strong>Dropdown No-Arrow, Chart Fixes & Dark Mode Flash Prevention</strong></p>
    <div class="docs-getstarted-code">
<pre><code>New:
  - sui-dropdown-no-arrow — modifier to hide dropdown caret arrow
    Works on .sui-dropdown wrapper or directly on .sui-dropdown-toggle

Fixes:
  - Horizontal bar chart: increase gap (8px → 14px) to prevent shadow overlap
  - Horizontal bar chart: widen label (60px → 80px) for longer text
  - Horizontal bar chart: fixed-width value column for equal track lengths
  - Password toggle: add :focus-visible outline for keyboard navigation
  - Fix e.target.closest TypeError on text nodes in speed dial hover

Docs:
  - Dark mode flash prevention guide in Getting Started
  - Recommended inline opacity:0 + blocking theme detection script</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 1.8.0 -->
  <section class="docs-getstarted-section" id="v1.8.0">
    <h2>v1.8.0</h2>
    <p><strong>Accessibility, Design Tokens & Quality of Life</strong></p>
    <div class="docs-getstarted-code">
<pre><code>Accessibility:
  - prefers-reduced-motion — disables all animations/transitions
  - Focus-visible on base links, sidebar nav, combobox, color picker
  - Color contrast improved — text-muted and text-light darkened to pass WCAG AA
  - Dropdown arrow key navigation (Up/Down to move, Escape returns focus)
  - Modal code examples updated with role="dialog", aria-modal, aria-labelledby
  - Table headers now include scope="col" in docs
  - Toast aria-atomic="true" for screen readers

Design Tokens:
  - dist/tokens.json — all design values as JSON
  - Documented in Theming guide with JS import and Tailwind examples

Docs:
  - Theming guide with full CSS variable reference
  - Dark mode toggle with localStorage + system preference detection
  - Changelog page with version history
  - Framework integration (React, Vue, Svelte, Astro, Next.js)
  - README updated with 60+ components and design tokens section

Fixes:
  - Page flash eliminated (inline opacity:0 until CSS loads)
  - Early theme detection in head (no dark mode flash)
  - Playground preview matches site theme by default
  - Sidebar scroll-to-active removed (caused flash)
  - Playground CSS moved to head (no FOUC)</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 1.7.0 -->
  <section class="docs-getstarted-section" id="v1.7.0">
    <h2>v1.7.0</h2>
    <p><strong>Utility Classes & New Components</strong></p>
    <div class="docs-getstarted-code">
<pre><code>New Components:
  - Tour / Walkthrough — spotlight overlay with step-by-step tooltips
  - Copy Button — click-to-copy with checkmark feedback
  - Text Rotate — animated word cycling (fade, slide, flip, zoom)
  - Typewriter — character-by-character typing with cursor styles
  - Marquee — infinite scrolling logos, text, cards
  - Browser Mockup — macOS/Windows chrome with tabs
  - Phone Mockup — notch, dynamic island, teardrop, punch hole

Utility Classes:
  - Display: inline, inline-block, grid
  - Position: relative, absolute, fixed, sticky + placement
  - Sizing: width, max-width, height, min/max
  - Overflow: hidden, auto, scroll, x/y variants
  - Opacity: 0 through 100
  - Z-Index: 0, 10, 20, 30, 40, 50
  - Cursor: pointer, not-allowed, grab, move, text
  - Visibility: visible, invisible, sr-only
  - Pointer Events, User Select

5 new utility docs pages.

Fixes:
  - Tour positioning and scroll-into-view
  - Brand hover color fix
  - Bento card tab focus (tabindex=-1 on preview elements)
  - Mobile drawer removed from tab order when closed</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>

